      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEROIC FEDERER (3) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 3 length win at this track in a handy 19.84. Has a low draw and goes well at this distance. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Can make it back-to-back wins. NUGGET ROBERTS (1) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind HEROIC FEDERER (20.06) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to feature again. AUSSIE MAC (2) promising dog unbeaten from two runs. Two of the wins have been this track and trip. Leading player again. OTHELLO (8) comes off a (20.00) win last time, scoring by 2.25 lengths in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Loves this draw, having won three of five starts.",
